</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uraypierre.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Raypierre</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 36<br> <font color=#E9D756>(11/27/01 11:38:11 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: VS (Re: Sagemon)</span><hr size=1> I'd like everyone to step back and take look at a few things here.<br>
<br>
1. Sage, I'm not going to repeat the arguements of anyone here. You are obviously so frustrated with the situation (as we all are) that argueing a point is not, going to get us anywhere any time soon. <br>
